stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Closed

    Closed: CLOSED (normal)\n- all requests pass through to AWS\n- count consecutive failures
    Open: OPEN (tripped)\n- reject all requests instantly\n- return HTTP 503\n- do NOT call AWS
    HalfOpen: HALF-OPEN (testing)\n- let 3 probe requests through\n- see if AWS has recovered

    Closed --> Open: 5 consecutive failures
    Open --> HalfOpen: after 15s cooldown
    HalfOpen --> Closed: all 3 probes succeed
    HalfOpen --> Open: any probe fails

    note right of Closed
        Filter: ConditionalCheckFailedException
        is expected business logic (409 on
        concurrent release) — NOT counted
        as a failure.
    end note
